{"_":143,"ana":144,"ref":145},{"layout":335},{"p":336,"rs":337,"damage":26},"Four lines of Latin, approximately centred with slightly inconsistent comma-shaped interpuncts. The lines are not perfectly horizontal or evenly spaced, with slightly irregular letters.",{"_":31,"ana":32,"ref":33},{"lettering":339,"dimensions":340},"Thinly carved letters with serfis and some curving flourishes, such as extended tail to the initial M. R in line 2 is open, whereas R in line 3 has a faint closing line. A has oblique cross bar descending to left. Interpunct end of line 2 is almost a hedera.",[341,343,346,348,352],{"type":38,"l":39,"from":40,"to":40,"h":342,"unit":42,"atLeast":342,"atMost":342},"30",{"type":38,"l":46,"from":47,"to":47,"h":344,"unit":42,"atLeast":345,"atMost":342},"25-30","25",{"type":38,"l":52,"from":53,"to":53,"h":347,"unit":42,"atLeast":345,"atMost":43},"25-29",{"type":38,"l":161,"from":162,"to":162,"h":349,"unit":42,"atLeast":350,"atMost":351},"23-24","23","24",{"type":58,"l":59,"from":40,"to":47,"unit":42},{"_":291,"notBefore":292,"notAfter":231,"evidence":170},[355,356],{"_":66,"type":67,"ref":68},{"_":71,"type":72,"ref":73},[358],[76,77],[299,300],{"_":82,"role":83,"ref":84},{"_":362,"type":86},"13ac",{"_":88,"mainLang":89,"languages":364},[88],"175698",{"n":93,"url":367,"height":95,"width":96,"desc":309,"surfaceType":98},"ISic000162_tiled.tif",[369,371,373,374],{"atLeast":370,"atMost":370},30,{"atLeast":372,"atMost":370},25,{"atLeast":372,"atMost":101},{"atLeast":375,"atMost":376},23,24,[110,111,112],[114,115,116],[380,381,382,15,19,143,121,122,123,124,122,125,126,89],"isic000162","epitaph for cornelius castor",{"_":12},"\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Dis\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"dis\">D(is)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-text=\"manibus\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"manes\">m